				<div id="post-5939" class="post-5939 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-survival-preparedness tag-gardening tag-organic-gardening tag-permaculture tag-soil tag-steve-solomon">
					<h1 class="entry-title">Episode-828- Steve Solomon on Organic Mythology and Soil Health</h1>

					<div class="entry-meta">
						<span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/steve-solomon-organic-mythology-soil-health" title="11:24 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">January 26, 2012</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/steve-solomon-organic-mythology-soil-health#comments" title="Comment on Episode-828- Steve Solomon on Organic Mythology and Soil Health">49 Comments</a></span>
											</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

					<div class="entry-content">
						<div id="tweetbutton5939" class="tw_button" style="float:right;margin-left:10px;"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fsteve-solomon-organic-mythology-soil-health&amp;text=Episode-828-%20Steve%20Solomon%20on%20Organic%20Mythology%20and%20Soil%20Health&amp;related=&amp;lang=en&amp;count=horizontal&amp;counturl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fsteve-solomon-organic-mythology-soil-health" class="twitter-share-button"  style="width:55px;height:22px;background:transparent url('http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-tweet-button/tweetn.png') no-repeat  0 0;text-align:left;text-indent:-9999px;display:block;">Tweet</a></div><div class="podPress_content podPress_content_audio_mp3">
